title: She Came On The Bus (1969-SWV)
description:
SHE CAME ON THE BUS
65 minutes

MPEG-4 rip from DVD-R, 1.35 mbbs

Originally released by Something Weird Video on a triple-feature disc with The Sin Syndicate and Sin Magazine.

Starring Linda Boyce, Ute Erickson, Jackie Roberts and a bunch of guys.

Adult juveniles romp through suburbia, invading a home or two, raping, shooting up, pillaging, getting their kicks. No one is safe. Then they hijack a bus and the party continues on the freeway, sort of like Magical Mystery Tour for hopheads and perverts. Very sleazy, released in the famous Summer of '69. 

There is a moralizing narrator and suspenseful library music.

Trailer also included.

Not a good movie, but it's a collector's item.
